cards.rules_text:
Kicker {4}{W}{W}
Invoke the Angels. [i](Begin or advance the Path of the Angel.)[/i]
If The Angel's Renown was kicked, create a white Avatar creature token with “This creature's power and toughness are each equal to your life total.”

Kicker {4}{U}{U}
Invoke the Sphinxes. [i](Begin or advance the Path of the Sphinx.)[/i]
If The Sphinx's Expertise was kicked, exile The Sphinx's Expertise, then take an extra turn after this one. You can't cast nonblue spells during that turn.

Kicker {3}{B}{B}
Invoke the Demons. [i](Begin or advance the Path of the Demon.)[/i]
If The Demon's Covenant was kicked, return up to two creature cards from your graveyard to your hand, then you may cast a black card from your hand by paying life equal to its mana value rather than paying its mana cost.

Kicker {3}{R}{R}
Invoke the Dragons. [i](Begin or advance the Path of the Dragon.)[/i]
If The Dragon's Majesty was kicked, add eight {R}. You can only cast two more spells this turn.

Kicker {3}{G}{G}
Invoke the Hydras. [i](Begin or advance the Path of the Hydra.)[/i]
If The Hydra's Persistence was kicked, untap up to two target Forests and put four +1/+1 counters on each of them. They become 0/0 green Hydra creatures with trample and hexproof. They're still lands.
